

F) REPLACE
============



—In Replace we can Provide the String After that the word which we want to Replace and at last We have to mention the word to which the string to be Replaced

[In the Below Example we Wanted to Replace World to MySQL]


SELECT REPLACE('Hello World', 'World', 'MySQL');  

+------------------------------------------+
| REPLACE('Hello World', 'World', 'MySQL') |
+------------------------------------------+
| Hello MySQL                              |
+------------------------------------------+







